## Checklist

- [ ] Master seed is configurable (env var or config file)
- [ ] All libraries are seeded from master seed
- [ ] `PYTHONHASHSEED` is set
- [ ] GPU determinism flags are enabled (if using GPU)
- [ ] Derived seeds are used for component independence
- [ ] Seeds are recorded in experiment output
- [ ] Reproducibility verification has been run
- [ ] Non-deterministic sources are documented with tolerance
